game_description: Demon Rush is a casual ragdoll arena brawler, heavily inspired by other arena combat games on VR. As banished hero, you are looking to fight your way out of the nether world. The demon hordes will do anything to keep you imprisoned, so you will have to use all the weapons at your disposal to fight your way out.
